    "The newer GPT-4 model performed better than its predecessor, the GPT-3.5-turbo, on all datasets except the Reddit dataset.",
    "On the Hate speech dataset, GPT-4 in particular performs on par with fine-tuned transformer models, suggesting that zero-shot classification can handle some tasks rather well.",
